OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fvery warm evening for many and staying
OL,7,Fsunny for most. Isolated thunderstorms
OL,8,Fare possible, mainly in the south,
OL,9,Fpotentially bringing large hail and
OL,10,Ffrequent lightning. Most places
OL,11,Fstaying entirely dry. Remaining rather
OL,12,Fwarm overnight with showers easing.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FAnother largely dry and
OL,15,Ffine day with plenty of sunshine.
OL,16,FFeeling quite a bit less hot than on
OL,17,FTuesday, with an easterly breeze, but
OL,18,Fstill very warm. Isolated showers
OL,19,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
